Dear Mr AZ Patient 3,

Ms AZ Patient 1 has invited you to access their medical information so you can help manage their health.

Message from Ms AZ Patient 1

Please be my carer.

To accept this invitation, click this link:

http://pkb-frontend-11/patient/accept.action?invitationId=4b55eb4f-a647-40b0-a176-e4c560261a41&e=az.patient.3%40pkbtest.com

You are receiving this notification because you are a carer. To log in and review the people you care for, please click this link: "http://pkb-frontend-11/patient/myDependents.action?tab=invitations&subTab=dependents"

Please do not reply to this email; this address is not monitored. Log into your record to manage your care and those whom you care for.

Yours,

Patients Know Best Help Team
